---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Contacto | DinamyCode"
  description="Listo para llevar tu negocio al próximo nivel - 3181252775"
>
  <section class="contact-hero bg-ink grid-bg">
    <div class="contact-hero__inner">
      <div class="contact-copy">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-dc-red text-xs font-semibold tracking-[.22em] uppercase">
          <span class="w-6 h-px bg-dc-red"></span>Contacto
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-paper leading-none">
          HABLEMOS DE TU PROXIMO PROYECTO
        </h1>
        <p>
          Cuéntanos qué necesitas construir, mejorar o automatizar. Te ayudamos a convertir esa idea en un plan claro para tu negocio.
        </p>
      </div>

      <address class="contact-card not-italic">
        <div>
          <span>Ubicacion</span>
          <p>Dg. 69c Sur #78C-36<br />Bogotá, Colombia</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>Telefono</span>
          <a href="tel:+573181252775" title="+573181252775">318 1252775</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>Correo</span>
          <a href="mailto:hola@dinamycode.com">hola@dinamycode.com</a>
        </div>
      </address>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-cta bg-dc-red overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none grid-bg"></div>

    <div class="relative w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-white reveal leading-none text-clamp-heading">
        ¿LISTO PARA LLEVAR<br />TU NEGOCIO<br />AL PROXIMO NIVEL?
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal text-white/75 mt-6">
        La primera consulta es sin costo. Hablemos hoy.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/573181252775"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="reveal mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-dc-red font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-paper transition-colors duration-300"
      >
        Escríbenos por WhatsApp →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .contact-hero {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem);
  }

  .contact-hero__inner {
    width: min(100%, 1120px);
    margin-inline: auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .contact-copy h1 {
    max-width: 10ch;
    margin-top: .85rem;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 12vw, 7rem);
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .contact-copy p {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: rgba(244, 243, 238, .82);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 1.5rem);
    border: 1px solid rgba(244, 243, 238, .12);
    border-radius: .75rem;
    background: rgba(19, 20, 42, .72);
  }

  .contact-card div {
    min-width: 0;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 243, 238, .08);
  }

  .contact-card div:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  .contact-card span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: .4rem;
    color: #90ffe8;
    font-size: .72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .contact-card p,
  .contact-card a {
    color: #f4f3ee;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 4vw, 1.75rem);
    line-height: 1.25;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  .contact-card a {
    transition: color .25s ease;
  }

  .contact-card a:hover {
    color: #90ffe8;
  }

  .contact-cta {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 7rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }

  .contact-cta p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.8vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-cta a {
    min-height: 3.25rem;
    padding: .95rem clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-size: clamp(.95rem, 2.8vw, 1rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 860px) {
    .contact-hero__inner {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(20rem, .9fr);
    }
  }
</style>
